ComicInfo.Summary: Having ventured deep into the Land of the East Wind, Dark finds himself cornered by the warriors of the Blue Dragon. In his fight with their leader, Leen, Dark has broken the Imperial edict that strictly prohibits battle between Phantom Saints. While their battle rages on, the rest of the warriors fear for their lives as the sheer power of Dark and Leen's vicious attacks destroys the land around them in the conclusion to the first story arc.
